Republic Italy places $ 1 . 5 bln on German debt mart . The Republic of Italy has completed a private placement of $ 1 . 5 billion on the German debt ( Schuldschein ) market with an duration of 16 years and a put option at the eighth year , the Italian Treasury said in a statement . The Treasury said the transaction had allowed the Republic to obtain a global interest rate of 5 . 985 percent for the first eight years and 6 . 189 percent for the entire duration . The placement was managed by JP Morgan , it said . - - Milan bureau + 392 66129507 
